  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can you outsmart chaos with perfect unit merges?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>ChanceLot TD: Merge Wars</i> is a unique tactical tower defense game where strategy, luck, and the art of merging units collide. Join exciting battles and team up with a friend or a random opponent to fend off waves of enemies together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/cc896c89314940e1249e98c1ff846d1f.poster.avif?t=1750754686\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/cc896c89314940e1249e98c1ff846d1f.webm?t=1750754686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/cc896c89314940e1249e98c1ff846d1f.mp4?t=1750754686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team Up to Defend Against Relentless Waves</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play cooperatively with a friend or a random ally as you defend your core against endless waves of increasingly powerful enemies. Coordination and timing are key to survival.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/b30f0ba8d8ced11e9b84c2297e70e43e.poster.avif?t=1750754686\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/b30f0ba8d8ced11e9b84c2297e70e43e.webm?t=1750754686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/b30f0ba8d8ced11e9b84c2297e70e43e.mp4?t=1750754686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Merge Units Mid-Battle for Tactical Advantage</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine identical units directly on the battlefield to unlock stronger forms with new abilities. Every merge opens the door to surprising power shifts and new strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/421adcbb237dee3dae00acbc579a1e97.poster.avif?t=1750754686\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/421adcbb237dee3dae00acbc579a1e97.webm?t=1750754686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/421adcbb237dee3dae00acbc579a1e97.mp4?t=1750754686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30+ Unique Units with Progression and Abilities</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and upgrade over 30 unique units, each with distinct stats, roles, and upgrade paths. Build the perfect team to suit your playstyle and counter any threat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/e4971b5ca72f6ca85327785cb52704fc.poster.avif?t=1750754686\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/e4971b5ca72f6ca85327785cb52704fc.webm?t=1750754686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639490/extras/e4971b5ca72f6ca85327785cb52704fc.mp4?t=1750754686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle Across Diverse Arenas</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight across a variety of dynamic environments, from lush forests to molten lava fields—each map offering different layouts, pacing, and strategic challenges.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Add to Your Wishlist Now!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t miss your chance to be part of the next big event in the tower defense genre! <strong>Add <i><u>ChanceLot TD: Merge Wars to your Steam Wishlist</u></i></strong> and be among the first to get notified when the game is released.</p>",
